Yes, I would also recommend Tomb. https://www.dyne.org/software/tomb/
via dyne.org / unsystem by Jaromil (https://github.com/jaromil).

Note:  It was mentioned earlier that there is TrueCrypt support in
cryptsetup.  I recommended using cryptsetup (if you are able to) but I
don't recommend TrueCrypt.
see https://github.com/bwalex/tc-play

